<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Update antique - Antique Collection</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Georgia:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f1e 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        .main-card {
            background: rgba(20, 20, 35, 0.8);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #2a2a4a;
            overflow: hidden;
            max-width: 1000px;
            width: 100%;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .row {
            display: flex;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .design-side {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0099ff 0%, #00d4ff 100%);
            color: #0f0f1e;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 60px 45px;
            text-align: center;
            min-height: 500px;
            flex: 0 0 45%;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .design-side h1 {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .design-side h2 {
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .design-side p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .form-side {
            padding: 60px;
            flex: 0 0 55%;
            background: rgba(20, 20, 35, 0.5);
        }

        .form-side h3 {
            color: #00d4ff;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .form-floating>label {
            color: #a0a0a0;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .form-floating>.form-control:focus~label,
        .form-floating>.form-control:not(:placeholder-shown)~label,
        .form-floating>.form-select:focus~label,
        .form-floating>.form-select:not(:placeholder-shown)~label {
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
        }

        .form-control,
        .form-select {
            background: rgba(30, 30, 50, 0.8) !important;
            border: 1.5px solid #2a2a4a !important;
            color: #e0e0e0 !important;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .form-control::placeholder {
            color: transparent;
        }

        .form-control:focus,
        .form-select:focus {
            border-color: #00d4ff !important;
            background: rgba(30, 30, 50, 0.95) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
            color: #e0e0e0 !important;
        }

        .form-select option {
            background-color: #1a1a2e;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        .btn-update {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0099ff);
            border: none;
            color: #0f0f1e;
            padding: 14px;
            font-weight: 800;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .btn-update:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
            color: #0f0f1e;
        }

        .btn-update:not(:hover) {
            color: #0f0f1e;
        }

        .back-link {
            text-align: center;
            display: block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #00d4ff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            color: #00ff88;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .design-side {
                flex: 0 0 100%;
                min-height: 300px;
                padding: 40px;
            }

            .design-side h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .form-side {
                flex: 0 0 100%;
                padding: 40px 30px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="main-card">
        <div class="row g-0">
            <div class="col design-side">
                <h1>‚úèÔ∏è</h1>
                <h2>Edit Details</h2>
                <p>Updating information ensures your Antique item database stays accurate and up-to-date.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col form-side">
                <h3>Update antique</h3>

                <form method="post" action="/updateantique">

                    <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= antique.id %>">

                    <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                        <input type="text" name="antique_name" class="form-control" id="fName"
                            value="<%= antique.antique_name %>" placeholder="antique Item Name" required>
                        <label for="fName">antique Item Name</label>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                        <input type="text" name="antique_age" class="form-control" id="fAuthor"
                            value="<%= antique.antique_age %>" placeholder="Age" required>
                        <label for="fAuthor">Antique Age (Years)</label>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row g-2 mb-3">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="form-floating">
                                <input type="number" name="antique_price" class="form-control" id="fPrice"
                                    value="<%= antique.antique_price %>" placeholder="Price" required>
                                <label for="fPrice">Price (‚Çπ)</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="form-floating">
                                <select class="form-select" name="antique_category" id="fLang"
                                    aria-label="Select Category" required>
                                    <option value="" disabled>Select Category</option>
                                    <option value="Furniture" <%=antique.antique_category==='Furniture' ? 'selected' : '' %>
                                        >ü™ë Furniture</option>
                                    <option value="Jewelry" <%=antique.antique_category==='Jewelry' ? 'selected' : '' %>>üíç
                                        Jewelry</option>
                                    <option value="Coins" <%=antique.antique_category==='Coins' ? 'selected' : '' %>>ü™ô
                                        Coins</option>
                                    <option value="Paintings" <%=antique.antique_category==='Paintings' ? 'selected' : '' %>
                                        >üñºÔ∏è Paintings</option>
                                    <option value="Clocks" <%=antique.antique_category==='Clocks' ? 'selected' : '' %>>‚è∞
                                        Clocks</option>
                                    <option value="Sculptures" <%=antique.antique_category==='Sculptures' ? 'selected' : ''
                                        %>>üóø Sculptures</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-floating mb-4">
                        <input type="text" name="antique_image" class="form-control" id="fImage"
                            value="<%= antique.antique_image %>" placeholder="Image Link" required>
                        <label for="fImage">Image üì∏ URL Link</label>
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-update w-100">Save Changes</button>
                    <a href="/?name=krushik" class="back-link">Cancel & Go Back</a>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

</body>

</html>